 
<p>

  Sanders: <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2023/apr/17/bernie-sanders-minimum-wage-living-wage">*We must raise the minimum wage to a living wage.*</a>
<p>
The necessities of life should not depend on employment.
If society provided those to everyone, the minimum wage would
not have to include that.

 